name: Anaerobic Capacity 1min & 2min
description:
This is a very high level of intensity that requires mental and physical perseverance. Along with improving your ability to produce sustained power above threshold, AC training will also enhance your ability to recover from high-intensity efforts and repeat them again and again. With 5 x 2min efforts followed by 3 x 1min efforts, you will need to stay focused today!
